      "span_text": "Therefore, in response to the above, Widrow et al. proposed an adaptive method for estimating the frequency content of a signal through demonstrating a relationship between the Discrete Fourier Transform (DFT) and the Least Mean Square (LMS) algorithm, where the DFT coefficients are estimated by a new means using the LMS algorithm"
